 Pleasure of Allah in pleasure of parents","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe pleasure of the Lord is in the pleasure of the parents, and the displeasure of the Lord is in the displeasure of the parents.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1899 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32033,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/salat-on-time-safe-lisan\/","url_meta":{"origin":33309,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salah: Best deed to pray on time","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which deeds are best?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer on time.\u201d I said, \u201cThen what, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cGood treatment of your parents.\u201d I said, \u201cThen what, O Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38326,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/07\/blessed-parents\/","url_meta":{"origin":33309,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Parents: Blessed is one who treats parents well","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 7, 2022","for